data.description: Open concept and vaulted ceilings ranch style home with walk-out basement on almost an acre. Lots of upgrades in this home including engineered hardwood floors (Acacia Wood) in living room, fireplace with rock face & raised hearth, custom bookcase & stereo component, new 6" custom made baseboards, revamped pantry with enlarged pantry shelves with small side cubbies and much more.  You will fall in love with the master bedroom/bath with its own private patio and hot tub. Downstairs master is very private with its own bath.  All bedrooms have their own bathrooms. Downstairs family/game room with wet bar.  New carpet & freshly painted.  Beautiful salt water pool with solar cover plus cabana with electricity.  Home has central air plus Breezair cooler and two furnaces.  Combined two small shops into one larger one with newer roof, metal siding and large wood door for rear entry.  Enough empty space to build an additional garage or larger shop.  City close but country feel.  No HOA
